   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ slug = design-complete
   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ question all, especially yourself
   в”‚  в””в”Ђ see the guide below
   в”‚
   в”њв”Ђ stillness рџЄ·
   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  so it is. a chance to slow down, breathe, and see clearly.
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  self review time is a sanctuary. a gift. a luxury not always available.
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  it is not every day one has a quiet moment to take a slow,
   в”‚  в”‚  methodical, patient, and thorough review.
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  tea first. then, we proceed рџЌµ
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в””в”Ђ
   в”‚
   в”њв”Ђ before you begin рџЄ·
   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  - clear your mind. this is dedicated review time.
   в”‚  в”‚  - open each artifact mentioned in the guide
   в”‚  в”‚  - read through them slowly, line by line
   в”‚  в”‚  - question every assumption made
   в”‚  в”‚  - look with fresh eyes, as if for the first time
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в””в”Ђ
   в”‚
   в”њв”Ђ here's the guide
   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  have you completed the full api design?
   в”‚  в”‚    are all endpoints, request/response shapes, and error cases documented?
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в””в”Ђ
   в”‚
   в”њв”Ђ after you finish рџЄ·
   в”‚  в”њв”Ђ
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в”‚  - did you check slowly, step by step?
   в”‚  в”‚  - did you take your time, or rush through?
   в”‚  в”‚  - have you been honest with yourself?
   в”‚  в”‚  - if you found issues, fix them before you promise
   в”‚  в”‚
   в”‚  в””в”Ђ
   в”‚
   в””в”Ђ promise its done? if so, run
      в””в”Ђ rhx route.stone.set --stone 3.blueprint --as promised --that design-complete
"
`;

